There are many good reasons to work in DevOps today.
DevOps is a growing industry in terms of job growth.
Also, the salaries in DevOps are higher than those in technology and computer science.
There is also a certain level of upward mobility in the DevOps career.
FACTS FOR FRUITS:
1 - Apples, peaches and raspberries are all members of the rose family. 
2 - Pumpkins and avocados are fruits not a vegetable.
 3 - A half-cup of figs has as much calcium as a half-cup of milk.
 4 - Green fruits help make your bones and teeth strong.
